      <hr><font face="Garamond, Times New Roman, serif", size=+1>
      <b><a name=design>Design notes:</a></b></font> <font face="Garamond, Times New Roman, serif">The overall design is based on Art Nouveau, 
      a style popular at the time radioactivity was discovered. Small design elements 
      are taken from <EM>Ready-to-Use Art Nouveau Small Frames and Borders</EM> 
      (Dover Clip-Art Series). The main font is Garamond; the large drop-in capital 
      letters are from Dan X. Solo, <EM>Ready-to-Use Art Nouveau Alphabets, </EM>also 
      published by Dover; the display font used elsewhere is ITC Benguiat. The 
      colors are inspired by the stained glass of Louis Comfort Tiffany.</font> 
